data.description: Don't miss the chance to explore this charming Townhome nestled in the picturesque Creekside Community. This residence showcases an appealing layout with not one, but two large primary suites! The ground floor greets you with a welcoming living area featuring a cozy fireplace, a convenient guest bathroom, a well-designed kitchen with abundant cabinet space, and an open dining area ideal for hosting gatherings. Step outside to your own secluded fenced patio, perfect for outdoor get-togethers. Ascend to the upper level, where you'll discover two spacious primary suites. Equally roomy, complete with an adjoining full bathroom and ample closets. Plus, you'll have the convenience of a two-car attached garage with a laundry area. The well-maintained community offers a pool and spa for your enjoyment. This residence is a must-see - don't let it slip away!
